            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "icon": "truck",
            "content": "<p>Shipping is calculated using standard shipping rates based on your location at check-out.<\/p><p><\/p><p>You have 30 days after receiving your item to request a return.<br\/><br\/>Please reach to us directly at <a href=\"mailto:thetidygnomestore@gmail.com\">nicecredenza@gmail.com<\/a> with your Order # to start a return.<\/p><p>To be eligible for a return, your item must be in the same condition that you received it, unworn or unused, with tags, and in its original packaging. You’ll also need the receipt or proof of purchase.<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible-row-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Dimensions",
            "icon": "ruler",
            "content": "",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible-row-3": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
